<blockquote class="gmail_quote" style="border-left: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0.8ex; padding-left: 1ex;"><div>Ah crumb - I found the problem. Sigh.<div><br></div><div>I actually fixed this in the trunk over 5 months ago when the problem first surfaced in my own testing, but it never came across to the stable release branch. The problem is that we weren&#39;t serializing the comm_spawn requests, and so the launch system gets confused over what has and hasn&#39;t completed launch. That&#39;s why it works fine on the trunk.</div>



